properties.Text: I used to be sad all the time. Then I learned that being angry is more productive.
For instance, if I was sad, I wouldn't have built this awesome maze for people like you. :)
Are you having fun? That's all I care about. :)
If you're getting frustrated, I could offer help. If you're not happy, I'm not happy. :)\n Take the one on the top-right.
The one on the bottom sends you all the way back to the start.
You're really close to the end now. Just take the one on the left.
Both of these exits are real. :)
